com.antigenomics.alisa.algebra.matrix

Class IndexedMatrixValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.antigenomics.alisa.algebra.matrix.IndexedMatrixValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IndexedValue<IndexedMatrixValue>, Serializable, Comparable<IndexedMatrixValue>

    public class IndexedMatrixValue
extends Object
implements IndexedValue<IndexedMatrixValue>
    An indexed matrix element. Contains real value, row and column indices. The comparison operation first compares the row index, the the column index, corresponding to linear indexing of an array with first row followed by second row and so on.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
